sentences: In 1997, Duro, DJ Clue, and Skane Dolla (DJ Clue's manager) developed Desert Storm Records.
In September 2001, Fabolous released his debut album Ghetto Fabolous, charting at No. 4 on the Billboard 200.
The label was previously distributed through Interscope, Elektra, Atlantic and Sony.
The label is currently distributed through Def Jam.
Recently, it was announced that Duro was appointed Senior VP of A&R at Republic Records.
